{
  "3181540": {
    "name": "Age of Wonders 4: Archon Prophecy",
    "steam_appid": 3181540,
    "required_age": "16",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《Age of Wonders 4: Archon Prophecy》</strong>扩展包中指挥光明势力<strong>。</strong>加入天界仲裁官的行列，与他们一起反击乌拉斯的腐败势力。占卜问卦，窥探决定王国命运的晦涩寓言，成为自己命运的主宰。包含新的文化、剧情内容及社会特性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新文化：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong><i>建筑师</i></strong>的帮助，建造您的帝国，在您的城市内建造巨大神奇的<strong><i>纪念碑</i></strong>，将其献给您选择的理念来增强您的经济，并解锁强力的加成。塑造您的领土并将您的意识形态刻进全世界之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/fbe8fe7462bcd88b87668ac22b41f19b.poster.avif?t=1759413818\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/fbe8fe7462bcd88b87668ac22b41f19b.webm?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/fbe8fe7462bcd88b87668ac22b41f19b.mp4?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两种新形态</strong>将永恒的斗争带至您帝国的灵魂之中：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>乐土之民</strong>：升至更高境界的天上人，为您的界域带来神圣加持。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>远古人</strong>：来自历史深处以及其他更邪恶场所的枯萎扭曲存在。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/ce58bd74c46d2a0f613d3426a26673ff.poster.avif?t=1759413818\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/ce58bd74c46d2a0f613d3426a26673ff.webm?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/ce58bd74c46d2a0f613d3426a26673ff.mp4?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新叙事内容：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong><i>预言特性</i></strong>铸造您的命运：这类新的社会特性能协助您塑造您的帝国。旅程初期，您将目睹一个异象，驱策您决定身为统治者的目标和野心。诠释的方式取决于您，但实现预言将解锁强大的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两个新剧情界域，一探神秘仲裁官的秘密：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>埃姆诺拉之环</strong>：进入仲裁官的大本营，隐密的埃姆诺拉界域，寻求援军加入对抗乌拉斯的无尽战争。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>索杜恩的峭壁</strong>：登陆索杜恩海岸，探索一片陷入幽影深渊无尽恐怖的古老之地。从乌拉斯的手中夺回界域，实现一个将塑造光明与黑暗之战的预言。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/dfb623aa1ee2ef8df6f94558c3e06756.poster.avif?t=1759413818\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/dfb623aa1ee2ef8df6f94558c3e06756.webm?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/dfb623aa1ee2ef8df6f94558c3e06756.mp4?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四本新魔典：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美德魔典</strong>：以坚定不移的正义增强您的军队，并巩固他们的战力直到最后一刻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>预言魔典</strong>：以能塑造战场的预言法术和预兆，将命运编织到每一个时刻之中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>亡灵魔典</strong>：引导死者的力量并对生者复仇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>仲裁官魔典</strong>：召唤星神盟友并将您的单位升级成仲裁官层级。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/2442b2e3a3a10ff89167a2ff8f013d84.poster.avif?t=1759413818\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/2442b2e3a3a10ff89167a2ff8f013d84.webm?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/2442b2e3a3a10ff89167a2ff8f013d84.mp4?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新英雄职业：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用<strong><i>战斗圣徒</i></strong>的力量回应神明的呼召。无论是作为神圣的支持单位引导信徒，还是作为殉道者般的坦克毫不退让，战斗圣徒都能化美德为力量、化牺牲为胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新野生动物单位：</strong>面对在各地出没的强大新种类野生动物。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 种星神动物</strong>：见识威武翱翔的格里芬，以及更雄伟的同类：星神格里芬。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 种仲裁官代表</strong>：仲裁官的精英使者。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 种亡灵仲裁官</strong>：败亡战士的扭曲残影，以死灵力量纠缠世界。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/65cc3eab62898c8a8ef107b612ea70a3.poster.avif?t=1759413818\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/65cc3eab62898c8a8ef107b612ea70a3.webm?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181540/extras/65cc3eab62898c8a8ef107b612ea70a3.mp4?t=1759413818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>额外内容：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 首全新配乐</strong>，由作曲家 Michiel van den Bos 制作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 种新坐骑：</strong>战车和格里芬。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新界面皮肤</strong>提供彻底沉浸的体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数项地图更新</strong>，包含一个新拾取物、一个新的远古奇观、一种新的侵扰以及一个新的区域种类。</p></li></ul>",
